# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ovora Cargo — Environment Variables Template
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development.
# Production values are managed by the cloud platform
# (Vercel / Netlify environment settings).
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Supabase — public keys (safe to expose in browser)
# These values are already hardcoded in utils/supabase/info.tsx
# Override here only if you fork the project with a new Supabase project.
# VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID=mkbcjxnoeevtkzaqcpsh
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<your-anon-key>

# Yandex Maps API key is loaded at runtime via Supabase Edge Function.
# Store it as a Supabase secret: supabase secrets set YANDEX_MAPS_API_KEY=<key>
# No frontend env var needed.
